{"tid":670041,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"睇黃子華不如睇陳志雲好過啦","createTime":"2018-05-19T04:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T06:24:13.000Z","uid":49163,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"164b2cb32d88a55e6765e963e2245a6e014a155a","tid":670041,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:22:50.000Z","msg":"人又靚仔d幽默d平d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又做過好多范見識廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要係有好多野爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢甘憎tvb今次仲唔有仇報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黃子華呢d吹大左不睇也罷<br />\n恰細路佢就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87590409722d241fb7ed0a277373807e79461837","tid":670041,"uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:24:27.000Z","msg":"【7月舉行演嘢會】陳志雲傘兵造型現身 請黎耀祥做嘉賓 (17:37)<br />\n2018/5/8<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/19/122422_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F19%2F122422_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9ca7796d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳志雲今日一身傘兵造型亮相記者會，並宣布會邀請黎耀祥任其中一晚嘉賓。（資料圖片/攝影：劉永銳）<br />\n<br />\n【今日直擊】陳志雲將於7月20至22日，假香港理工大學賽馬會綜藝館，舉行《志雲尋志雲 登陸舞台演嘢會》，今日志雲大師以傘兵造型，現身記者會，期間還大擺甫士，非常神似。<br />\n<br />\n好友王喜擔任司儀，他見到陳志雲「典地」時，不禁說：「又不是溫碧霞演唱會，你『典地』幹甚麼？」陳志雲即作狀扮打王喜，還禁不住揶揄對方。<br />\n<br />\n嘉賓方面，陳志雲透露會有曾俊華、田北俊、陶傑、謝安琪及張繼聰等，他還特別提及黎耀祥，指與對方關係深長。王喜即反問：「我跟他誰比較長？」陳志雲笑說：「視乎角度和功能性。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1525772253934&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1525772253934%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180508&d=QhqAE%2BowGebsppo1Z3Gpx%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ad252656\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1525772253934%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180508&h=33372c43\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1525772253934&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180508</a>"},{"pid":"2a25e6dce4bea454b3b74526f8e6aad68c9e8814","tid":670041,"uid":5843,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"睇陳志雲不如睇黃洋達好過啦"},{"pid":"634aafa5beb0693d4b477db39263256fabe4cedb","tid":670041,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:42:19.000Z","msg":"啊雲同啊喜 好撚基"},{"pid":"1c5360a855b71e517c76c3ff344d030bccf001fc","tid":670041,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"gay 佬 不了"},{"pid":"c3492d52facbf0128a70cd9e1a7a908c4fa5cf5f","tid":670041,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"634aafa5beb0693d4b477db39263256fabe4cedb","tid":670041,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:42:19.000Z","msg":"啊雲同啊喜 好撚基"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"幾有趣"},{"pid":"3168e1adfb4b5d30a516a759fc261b354929d45f","tid":670041,"uid":49163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a25e6dce4bea454b3b74526f8e6aad68c9e8814","tid":670041,"uid":5843,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"睇陳志雲不如睇黃洋達好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"唔好拎垃圾同大師比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11f64c93a9c63516e020deb4f17b672f5d530c8d","tid":670041,"uid":9803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"164b2cb32d88a55e6765e963e2245a6e014a155a","tid":670041,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:22:50.000Z","msg":"人又靚仔d幽默d平d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又做過好多范見識廣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink